        <mxCell id="capacity" value="&lt;b&gt;Capacity overview&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;App cluster: 3 узла × (16GB RAM, 8 vCPU, 1TB SSD) = 48GB / 24 vCPU&lt;br/&gt;Data cluster: 2 узла Postgres × (32GB, 8 vCPU, 4TB NVMe) + 4 узла MinIO × (8GB, 4 vCPU, 8TB)&lt;br/&gt;DR: пропорционально primary / 2&lt;br/&gt;Bastion: 1 узел × (4GB, 2 vCPU, 100GB)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;HA matrix&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Postgres: RTO &lt; 5s · RPO &lt; 1s (sync)&lt;br/&gt;MinIO: EC 4+2 · до 2 узлов потеряем без deg&lt;br/&gt;Keycloak: 2 active-active с shared DB&lt;br/&gt;DR: RTO 4h · RPO 5min" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fafafa;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
